7
00:00:49,233 --> 00:00:50,324
Mama.

8
00:00:53,273 --> 00:00:54,529
Bola si to ty, mama?

9
00:01:05,483 --> 00:01:06,779
Eul Chook.

10
00:01:37,543 --> 00:01:40,135
<i>Philip, si zranený?</i>

11
00:01:43,754 --> 00:01:45,519
<i>Vrátim ti všetko, čo si...</i>

12
00:01:46,124 --> 00:01:47,756
