696
00:58:01,607 --> 00:58:03,892
Neviem, čo povedala Yoon Ah, ale ja...

697
00:58:08,847 --> 00:58:10,071
Bojím sa.

698
00:58:18,228 --> 00:58:19,248
V ten deň

699
00:58:21,398 --> 00:58:23,610
